<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我可是深有体会的</b></font>

126
00:08:40,890 --> 00:08:43,100
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>磕头是毫无意义的</b></font>

127
00:08:43,560 --> 00:08:45,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我打从心底里清楚这一点</b></font>

128
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:51,990
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>处于困境中的人来苦苦哀求我时 我总是无法弃之不顾</b></font>

129
00:08:52,410 --> 00:08:55,160
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>总是会不断借钱给他们</b></font>

130
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,910
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>因为我想救他们嘛</b></font>

131
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:01,460
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但结果却是吃尽苦头</b></font>

132
00:09:02,290 --> 00:09:06,420
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>明明是双方同意才签的约</b></font>

133
00:09:06,630 --> 00:09:10,570
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>到了还钱的时候 他们总是能若无其事的赖帐</b></font>

134
00:09:11,670 --> 00:09:17,600
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>当然表面上还是显得很抱歉 并且会磕头认错</b></font>

135
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,060
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>求您了 再给我...</b></font>

136
00:09:19,140 --> 00:09:23,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>为什么我都这么努力道歉了 这家伙还不原谅我</b></font>

137
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:28,720
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>心里却是这样责骂着我 并骂我是冷血无情的家伙</b></font>

138
00:09:30,690 --> 00:09:32,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你不觉得很过分吗</b></font>

139
00:09:33,660 --> 00:09:37,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>显然这些人道歉时根本没有诚意</b></font>

140
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:40,250
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>再说了 在借贷中的所谓诚意</b></font>

141
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:44,040
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这个无论让谁来评都只有一条</b></font>

142
00:09:44,370 --> 00:09:47,340
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那就是 不管做什么都好</b></font>

143
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:50,810
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>要在规定期限内还清欠款</b></font>

144
00:09:52,970 --> 00:09:55,010
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>除此之外还有什么诚意可言</b></font>

145
00:09:57,010 --> 00:10:02,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没错 还不出钱的同时他们就已经没有了诚意</b></font>

146
00:10:06,220 --> 00:10:10,830
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>而其证据就是 在磕头一事上稍微增加点负担</b></font>

147
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:15,500
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他们就已经无法好好道歉了</b></font>

148
00:10:19,570 --> 00:10:21,940
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>本来 应该是可以办到的</b></font>

149
00:10:22,070 --> 00:10:25,140
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果心里真的充满了歉意</b></font>

150
00:10:25,210 --> 00:10:27,710
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>无论在哪都应该可以磕头认错</b></font>

151
00:10:28,180 --> 00:10:34,630
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>即便是在会烤肉烧骨的铁板上也一样</b></font>

152
00:10:37,890 --> 00:10:40,970
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这才是诚意啊</b></font>

153
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:44,130
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>对吧 利根川</b></font>

154
00:11:01,420 --> 00:11:04,540
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>其实不用向你多加说明了吧</b></font>

155
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:07,500
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不过以防万一我还是说一下</b></font>

156
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:12,760
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这烤肉磕头为了证明谢罪一方的诚意</b></font>

157
00:11:13,140 --> 00:11:17,010
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>至少也要头碰铁板10秒以上</b></font>

158
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:21,390
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这10秒从额头碰到铁板的瞬间开始计算</b></font>

159
00:11:22,520 --> 00:11:27,020
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果磕不够10秒的话就要重磕</b></font>

160
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:31,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>要再道一次歉 从头开始</b></font>

161
00:11:35,450 --> 00:11:41,760
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不断重来直到磕足10秒为止</b></font>

162
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:49,250
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>即使烧化了额头上的皮肉 直接烤头盖骨也一样</b></font>

163
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:53,380
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你一副何必做到这种地步的表情嘛</b></font>

164
00:11:54,930 --> 00:11:57,430
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是 不这么做就是不行</b></font>

165
00:11:57,930 --> 00:12:02,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>谢罪这种行为 越是痛苦也就越能显示真价值</b></font>

166
00:12:03,190 --> 00:12:08,770
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>只有忍受了这种痛苦才能证明 所谓的诚意</b></font>

167
00:12:11,070 --> 00:12:12,490
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>应该可以办到的</b></font>

168
00:12:12,570 --> 00:12:17,910
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果胸中真的满怀歉意真心想道歉的话</b></font>

169
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,660
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>应该能道歉的</b></font>

170
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:22,500
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不 不道歉甚至觉得坐立难安</b></font>

171
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:27,830
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这既能洗刷开司你的伙伴们的悔恨</b></font>

172
00:12:28,420 --> 00:12:32,630
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>同时也是对因他蒙羞的我的正当的道歉</b></font>

173
00:12:34,590 --> 00:12:37,970
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>理所当然 这种程度是理所当然的</b></font>

174
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:41,520
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>诚意就是这么严厉的</b></font>

175
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:46,690
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>怎么样 利根川 你会让我们看到吧</b></font>

176
00:12:47,350 --> 00:12:50,920
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>诚意 真正的诚意</b></font>

177
00:12:54,930 --> 00:12:57,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>果然没办法自己主动完成吗</b></font>

178
00:12:58,270 --> 00:12:58,820
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>喂</b></font>

179
00:12:59,000 --> 00:12:59,430
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是</b></font>

180
00:12:59,830 --> 00:13:00,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可以准备了</b></font>

181
00:13:07,540 --> 00:13:11,750
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我真的很喜欢这玩意</b></font>

182
00:13:15,010 --> 00:13:16,760
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>强制磕头机</b></font>

183
00:13:21,890 --> 00:13:23,790
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>住手 求你了</b></font>

184
00:13:24,020 --> 00:13:25,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我一定会还钱的</b></font>

185
00:13:27,190 --> 00:13:29,730
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>对于不还钱的不正之徒</b></font>

186
00:13:29,900 --> 00:13:31,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就把他们绑上这机器</b></font>

187
00:13:32,070 --> 00:13:33,610
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>强制他们磕头认错</b></font>

188
00:13:37,860 --> 00:13:41,490
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是 对于都帮他摆好了姿势</b></font>

189
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:44,580
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>却还是无法磕头认错的无耻之徒</b></font>

190
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,620
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就将强制实行诚意</b></font>

191
00:13:48,250 --> 00:13:51,690
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>如果安分一点的话 被烧的就只有额头而已</b></font>

192
00:13:52,250 --> 00:13:54,790
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>因为要挣扎 所以整张脸都被烧烂</b></font>

193
00:13:55,190 --> 00:13:57,520
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>昏迷 失禁</b></font>

194
00:14:09,230 --> 00:14:11,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>差不多可以上了</b></font>

195
00:14:12,060 --> 00:14:15,150
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开始吧 烤肉磕头</b></font>

196
00:14:17,490 --> 00:14:18,200
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>别碰我</b></font>

197
00:14:18,680 --> 00:14:19,980
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不许碰我</b></font>

198
00:14:21,550 --> 00:14:23,420
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我自己来就行了吧</b></font>

199
00:14:24,020 --> 00:14:24,850
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我自己来</b></font>

200
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:31,120
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>当然了 当然这是最好不过了</b></font>

201
00:14:31,830 --> 00:14:33,490
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不过啊 利根川</b></font>

202
00:14:33,630 --> 00:14:40,800
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>正如你所知 还没有凭自己的意志能在这烤肉磕头中坚持十秒的</b></font>

203
00:14:41,380 --> 00:14:44,300
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我劝你还是不要逞强的好</b></font>

204
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:49,610
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>万一失败的话可是要烤好多次脸的</b></font>

205
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,780
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>拿开 把那机器拿开</b></font>

206
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:32,480
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>利根川</b></font>

207
00:16:01,010 --> 00:16:02,880
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这让人感觉仿佛是永远似的十秒</b></font>

208
00:16:03,340 --> 00:16:06,800
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>充斥着腐臭与惨叫的十秒</b></font>

209
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:09,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>醒不了的噩梦</b></font>

210
00:16:10,850 --> 00:16:12,270
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>恶魔的欢乐时光</b></font>

211
00:16:12,680 --> 00:16:13,600
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>地狱</b></font>

212
00:16:18,970 --> 00:16:19,970
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>才刚过了4秒</b></font>

213
00:16:29,530 --> 00:16:32,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>利根川 利根川</b></font>

214
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,540
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>怎么可能 这算什么</b></font>

215
00:16:37,170 --> 00:16:38,420
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这算什么眼泪</b></font>

216
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:43,210
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可恶...可恶...</b></font>

217
00:16:46,010 --> 00:16:50,970
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>结果 利根川在这活生生的地狱里待了12秒</b></font>

218
00:16:51,220 --> 00:16:55,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>到达了极限 在完成之后 他许久都无法动弹</b></font>

219
00:16:55,350 --> 00:16:57,940
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>将患处冷却 用毛巾治疗过后</b></font>

220
00:16:58,150 --> 00:17:00,320
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>由别人扶着好不容易才站起来</b></font>

221
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>离开房间</b></font>

222
00:17:03,310 --> 00:17:06,150
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是 利根川成功了</b></font>

223
00:17:06,990 --> 00:17:08,570
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>完成了烤肉磕头</b></font>

224
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:24,300
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我错了</b></font>

225
00:17:25,550 --> 00:17:26,300
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我...</b></font>

226
00:17:27,130 --> 00:17:29,590
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>错了是...指什么</b></font>

227
00:17:30,340 --> 00:17:32,270
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>利根川并不是我真正的敌人</b></font>

228
00:17:32,770 --> 00:17:33,810
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>只是个傀儡</b></font>

229
00:17:34,850 --> 00:17:38,140
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>他也和我们一样 其实只是被利用着而已</b></font>

230
00:17:39,230 --> 00:17:41,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>被那个男人 会长利用着</b></font>

231
00:17:43,270 --> 00:17:47,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不打倒会长的话 就不算为石田他们报了仇</b></font>

232
00:17:48,860 --> 00:17:52,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>哦...也不是不明白你的心情</b></font>

233
00:17:52,790 --> 00:17:54,910
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不过 这也没办法的啦</b></font>

234
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:57,790
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我没有赢 没有赢</b></font>

235
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:59,570
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没这种事啦</b></font>

236
00:17:59,730 --> 00:18:01,630
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你已经赢了很多了</b></font>

237
00:18:02,040 --> 00:18:03,670
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>所以才有这笔钱啊</b></font>

238
00:18:05,170 --> 00:18:06,170
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这...</b></font>

239
00:18:06,970 --> 00:18:09,300
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>只是为会长表演节目的出场费</b></font>

240
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:10,340
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是报酬</b></font>

241
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:12,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>报酬 不也好吗</b></font>

242
00:18:12,710 --> 00:18:14,510
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>钱就是钱啊 没区别的</b></font>

243
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:18,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司你不也是为了钱而奋战至今吗</b></font>

244
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:20,520
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不 钱只是一半原因</b></font>

245
00:18:20,850 --> 00:18:22,400
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我并不全是为了钱</b></font>

246
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:26,430
